text: Galina Kamenova (born 16 September 1970) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Vratsa
